muxi.pwps.sdk.service

Interface PWPSInitListener


  • public interface PWPSInitListener
    Interface used to notify SDK the result of init solicitation It is notify when the initialization process had some problem or it is finalized

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onInitError()
      The initialization process had problem and it is necessary to redo this operation to start using POSWEB Pay Services
      void onInitSuccess()
      The initialization process occurs without any problem, and the service is prepared to be used
